flowchart TD
    Start([Proposal Submitted]) --> Discussion[Discussion Phase<br/>7-14 days]
    Discussion --> Voting[DAO Voting<br/>Token-Weighted]
    Voting --> VoteCheck{Vote Result}
    VoteCheck -->|Rejected| Reject[Proposal Rejected]
    VoteCheck -->|Approved| Execution[Execution Phase]
    Execution --> ExecType{Type}
    ExecType -->|Contract| Auto[Auto Execute]
    ExecType -->|Treasury| Treasury[Treasury Release]
    ExecType -->|Project| Project[IPI Pipeline]
    Auto --> Record[Blockchain Record]
    Treasury --> Record
    Project --> Record
    Record --> End([Complete])
    Reject --> End
